<br>
People don't wanna be at a loot camp that isn't amazing exp if they don't have a realistic shot at loot and since most loot camps don't have a little something for everyone, you will either have to either promise them a roll on it or something else in return such as helping with a future camp of their own.<br>
<br>
People should still try to make NBG work however because i'd much rather tell a cool story of how i got my fighting baton myself rather then a story about how i won caster loot, instead of the caster in the group, and sold it for the pp to buy a fighting baton off some famer. Getting your own shit yourself, and at a level where it is challenging, is one of the best feelings you can have playing this game.<br>
